posting_body: ['EdgePoint', '320 N 85th Street, Seattle, WA, 98103', 'Want more info on this unit?', 'See the link (below):', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 34', 'OR Text', '34', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our team.', 'Find Your New Home Today!', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 980 -1018', 'Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Discover your new home at EdgePoint in Seattle’s Greenwood neighborhood!', 'Our new apartment home community includes open one bedrooms, traditional one bedrooms, one bedrooms with dens & two bedrooms!', 'Homes will feature designer finishes including stainless steel appliances, quartz counter tops, walk-in closets* & mountain views*.', 'Community amenities include a rooftop deck with mountain views, clubroom, fitness center, bike storage, pet spa, dog run and electric vehicle parking.', 'Being located in the heart of Greenwood your favorite grocery stores, shopping and dining are just steps away.', 'We can’t wait to welcome you home to EdgePoint!', 'Features', '- A/C Ports*', '- Stainless Steel Appliances', '- Quartz Countertops', '- In-Unit Washer and Dryer', '- Patio*', '- Mountain Views*', '- Walk-in Closets*', '- Balcony*', '*select apartment homes', 'Community Amenities', '- Pet Wash and Dog Run', '- Electric Vehicle Parking', '- Club Room', '- Resident and Bike storage', '- Fitness Center', '- Rooftop Fire Pits and BBQ', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet friendly', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'S761ITtOBdBp']
